            <p class="open-sans w-full text-xs text-justify text-white font-light sm:text-center lg:text-sm 2xl:text-lg">Founded in February 1995, BYD is a high-tech company devoted to leveraging technological innovations for a better life. After more than 27 years of high-speed growth, BYD has established over 30 industrial parks across 6 continents and played a significant role in industries related to electronics, auto, renewable energy and rail transit. With a focus on energy acquisition, storage, and application, BYD offers comprehensive new energy solutions with zero-emission.</p>
